title: Sisters 2
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In a small town with little vegetarian food, this cafe and bakery is a good option as it is clean and cheerful and the owner, who speaks English, will accommodate veg requests. Serves breakfast and baked goods, pumpkin pancake, coffee, tea, fruit smoothies. Free Wi-Fi. Directions: No street names or numbers, just go towards the river at the 2000 monument, and it's on the left hand side of the road.
streetAddress: On the road from the 2000 statue, towards the riverfront
